Package com.sugarcrm.candybean.datasource

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CSV
    CSV class parses an input csv file.
    CsvDataAdapter
    CsvDataAdapter is used by client to convert csv files into a list of DataSource.
    DataAdapter
    DataAdapter is an interface class a client uses to convert csv, xml, etc.
    DataAdapterFactory
    DataAdapterFactory is a public interface used to get various DataAdapters.
    DataSource
    DataSource models a file containing a list of records.
    DS  
    FieldSet
    FieldSet is the basic type returned by the DataAdapter from converting the original csv, xml, etc.
